  subtitleLines:
  - text: I rushed along this hard road for years,
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: too worn to gaze at the moon.
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: "I sought life\u2019s faint hidden meaning,"
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: chasing goals that faded soon.
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: I chose to raise a cat,
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: to let a new life in my life croon.
    delayAfter: 100
